# db-grid-vue

Vue 3 wrapper for DB Grid - High-performance Angular data grid component

## Peer Dependencies

- **Vue**: `^3.2.0`

This package requires the DB Grid Web Component to be loaded separately:

```html
<!-- index.html -->
<script src="https://unpkg.com/db-grid/dist/db-grid.min.js"></script>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/db-grid/dist/db-grid.css">
```

## Vue Version Support

| Vue Version | Supported |
|-------------|-----------|
| Vue 3.2+  | ✅ Yes     |
| Vue 2.x    | ❌ No      |

## Quick Start

```bash
npm install db-grid-vue
```

See [README.md](./README.md) for full documentation.
